<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>New Cour Added</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>New Cour Added</h2>
    <p>Hello {{ user.nomUser }},</p>
    <p>A new cour has been added:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Title: {{ cour.titreCours }}</li>
        <li>Description: {{ cour.descriCours }}</li>
        <li>Date: {{ cour.datedebutCours|date('Y-m-d') }} to {{ cour.datefinCours|date('Y-m-d') }}</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Thank you for being a part of our platform.</p>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>Your Organization</p>
</body>
</html>
